# Cloud Service Models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS)
- IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service) -> AWS EC2, Google Compute Engine OS and Apps
- PaaS (Platform as a Service) -> Heroku, Google App Engine only Code
- SaaS (Software as a Service) -> Gmail, Salesforce, Dropbox nothing but settings

# Cloud Deployment Models
- Public Cloud -> Shared many, cheap, efficient -> AWS, Azure, Google Cloud (GCP)
- Private Cloud -> personal, secure, expensive -> on-premise
- Hybrid Cloud -> private space, public infrastructure -> public and private together
- Multi-Cloud - AWS and Azure at the same time

